Name: Senior Staff: Team Leader
Desc: An Interastral Peace Corporation senior staff member with a minimal rank of project team leader. The mech they drive belongs to the IPC. If damaged, its repair fees have to be paid out-of-pocket. With a half-decent salary, they can at least afford to rent a one-bedroom apartment on one of the IPC's enterprise ships.

SkillList.SkillDesc: Deals minor Physical DMG to a single target.
Deals Physical DMG to a single target.
Enters the Charging state. Uses Work Culture Shock in the next action.
Deals Physical DMG to all targets.
Seizes all Performance Points from Grunt: Field Personnel and Grunt: Security Personnel.
Summons Grunt: Field Personnel or Grunt: Security Personnel, then cause all Grunts: Field Personnel and Grunts: Security Personnel to acquire 1 Performance Point.
Receives 1 Performance Point after unleashing an attack. Performance Points can be seized by the attacker when this unit's Weakness is Broken or this unit receives a killing blow.
